ce/GetAds,14,transport is closing,出现次数:1\n", "matched_anomaly": "A fault occurred from 2025-06-24T08:10:37Z to 2025-06-24T08:25:37Z. Please identify the root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-24 08:10:37+00:00 to 2025-06-24 08:25:37+00:00"}, "trace_data_collected": true, "log_analysis_findings": "基于对故障时间段日志数据的分析，我已经完成了初始扫描。以下是分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"connection refused\", \"transport is closing\", \"transport\", \"Error while dialing\", \"dial tcp\", \"Unavailable\", \"rpc error\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"adservice 服务出现连接拒绝和端口配置错误，导致 frontend 服务无法建立连接\",\n      \"evidence\": \"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.8.174:9555: connect: connection refused\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"frontend 服务在调用 adservice 时遇到大量 RPC 连接问题，包括连接拒绝和传输关闭错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to get ads: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = transport is closing\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 分析要点：\n\n1. **主要错误模式**：\n   - 所有错误日志都来自 `frontend` 服务\n   - 错误集中在调用 `adservice` 获取广告数据时\n   - 出现两种主要错误类型：`connection refused` 和 `transport is closing`\n\n2. **关键发现**：\n   - 目标 IP `10.233.8.174:9555` 反复出现连接拒绝\n   - 故障涉及所有 frontend 实例（frontend-0, frontend-1, frontend-2）\n   - 错误发生时间集中在 08:10:37Z 到 08:12:41Z\n\n3. **根因推测**：\n   - **Port Misconfiguration 可能性高**：基于 `connection refused` 错误模式，可能是 adservice 端口配置错误\n   - **服务宕机可能性**：adservice 可能在该时间段内宕机或重启\n\n需要进一步获取 adservice 的日志和健康状态信息来确认根因。", "trace_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"frontend->frontend\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"frontend->cartservice\",\n    \"recommendationservice->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"AdService\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"频繁出现连接错误（connection refused），错误码为14，出现次数超过1000次。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"从checkoutservice调用cartservice的GetCart操作，平均延迟从8152.6ms增加到21906.175ms，延迟倍数约为2.7倍。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"从cartservice调用redis的HGET操作，平均延迟从1739.74ms增加到8195.53ms，延迟倍数约为4.7倍。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"从frontend调用productcatalogservice的GetProduct操作，平均延迟从10040.37ms增加到10834.96ms，延迟倍数约为1.08倍。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"从checkoutservice调用shippingservice的GetQuote操作，平均延迟从214.27ms增加到775.0ms，延迟倍数约为3.6倍。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于对故障时间段 2025-06-24T08:10:37Z 到 2025-06-24T08:25:37Z 的指标数据全面扫描分析，我发现了多个显著的异常调用链。以下是分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"rrt_max\", \"rrt\", \"response\", \"request\", \"node_memory_usage_rate\", \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"cpu_usage\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio和client_error_ratio异常飙升，p99变化率分别达到2.0和2.0，表明该Pod出现严重错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio: 正常p99=0.0, 故障p99=0.85; client_error_ratio: 正常p99=0.0, 故障p99=0.85\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max和rrt指标显著恶化，p99变化率分别达到1.7205和1.245，响应时间大幅增加\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max: 正常p99=4176.8, 故障p99=55607.0; rrt: 正常p99=2478.68, 故障p99=10653.85\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"response和request指标异常，中位数变化率分别达到1.8202和1.8189，请求处理量急剧下降\",\n      \"evidence\": \"response: 正常中位数=1020.0, 故障中位数=48.0; request: 正常中位数=1012.0, 故障中位数=48.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-07\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_memory_usage_rate异常升高，中位数从28.73%上升到35.21%，内存使用率显著增加\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_usage_rate: 正常中位数=28.73%, 故障中位数=35.21%, 变化率=0.2027\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes显著减少，可用内存从10.09GB下降到8.46GB，内存资源紧张\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes: 正常中位数=10090201088.0, 故障中位数=8461967360.0, 变化率=0.1755\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tikv\",\n      \"reason\": \"cpu_usage指标异常升高，中位数从0.09上升到0.11，数据库CPU负载增加\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cpu_usage: 正常中位数=0.09, 故障中位数=0.11, 变化率=0.2\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现总结**：\n1. **服务级故障**: checkoutservice-1出现严重错误率飙升，paymentservice-1响应时间显著恶化\n2. **节点级资源压力**: aiops-k8s-07和aiops-k8s-08节点内存使用异常\n3. **数据库性能问题**: tidb-tikv组件CPU使用率上升\n4. **服务降级**: adservice-2请求处理量急剧下降\n\n需要进一步深入分析这些异常之间的因果关系，特别是节点资源压力是否对服务性能产生了级联影响。"}
